<h1>Hosting Signup</h1>
<p>Just click the "buy" now button on the payment page and email ckdake at ckdake dot com the info about what you want hosted. What websites and subdomains, what additional services (subversion, Chandler, etc) you want and usernames desired for them, what you'd like your SSH username(s) to be, any e-mail addresses that ithought should host as well as any that get forwarded somewhere else, and anything else you can think of. You'll get an email back with any more information needed or instructions for you, and generally you will be up and running within 30 minutes of getting ithought all the required information. Sometimes it takes longer at night or on weekends.</p>
